Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,*************** INTRO ***************
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,*************** EPISODE ***************
Comment: 0,0:04:05.40,0:04:13.21,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,
Comment: 0,0:22:53.28,0:23:05.33,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.96,0:00:08.36,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Once there was a man who obtained everything,\Nthe legendary Pirate King Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.36,0:00:12.91,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,His last words before he was executed inspired people to sail the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.91,0:00:14.63,Gold,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,All my wealth and treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.63,0:00:16.27,Gold,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,It can be yours if you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.27,0:00:17.42,Gold,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,Search for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.42,0:00:19.79,Gold,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,I left everything in that one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:22.82,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,People now set sail in search of romance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.82,0:00:25.40,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The world has entered a Great Age of Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.05,0:02:40.01,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,All pirates who seek One Piece\Nstrive to reach the second half of the Grand Line...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.01,0:02:42.55,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The place called the New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.68,0:02:51.27,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,However, the only one who ever conquered that ocean\Nwas the Pirate King, Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.20,0:02:57.57,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has killed\Nthe dreams and ambitions of countless pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.08,0:03:03.45,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,And now, the boy who ate the Gomu Gomu Fruit\Nand became a rubber man,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:07.20,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy and his crew\Nare going to challenge that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.69,0:03:11.27,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.82,0:03:17.38,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,In order to reach their next stage, the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.38,0:03:20.60,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and the other Straw Hat Pirates have gone to Fishman Island,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.60,0:03:22.78,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,located ten thousand meters under the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.61,0:03:28.87,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,But there they find that the New Fishman Pirates\Nare planning to overthrow the Ryuuguu Kingdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.87,0:03:33.02,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,and Vander Decken has been stalking the Mermaid Princess Shirahoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.02,0:03:37.86,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hat Pirates find themselves drawn into these events.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:42.00,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,If I join the Seven Warlords,\Nthe Government will pardon my crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.00,0:03:49.20,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Aladdin and others who want to quit being pirates\Nwill be able to live in this country in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:52.25,Main,Arlong,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother died!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:55.08,Main,Macro,0000,0000,0000,,We're also going back to\Ndoing our own thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.78,0:03:58.35,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,The Sun Pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.35,0:04:00.82,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,split into three groups,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.82,0:04:05.40,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,and everybody went their own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.33,0:04:23.78,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,We're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.29,0:04:27.83,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it...\NI never thought this day would come!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:31.47,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Back in the days when the Celestial Dragons were working us to the bone,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.47,0:04:35.25,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,we could only silently curse them in despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.25,0:04:39.74,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to Brother Ti,\Nwe were able to escape from the Celestial Dragons...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.74,0:04:42.01,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,but we were still wanted men.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:45.60,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,I thought our only choice was to live as pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.60,0:04:50.51,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,But today, we can finally return to our birthplace and be accepted with open arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.51,0:04:53.30,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,We're free at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:58.19,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Captain... No, Brother Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:05:00.23,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,We'll never forget what you've done for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.23,0:05:02.32,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,You're exaggerating.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.32,0:05:05.40,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,No, we all understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.40,0:05:09.78,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,In order to be free,\Nwe needed a pardon from the Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.78,0:05:12.76,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why you joined the Seven Warlords.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.76,0:05:15.50,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you wanted to join them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:20.71,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,How about you stop talking nonsense and hurry on back to your families?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:23.88,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Look.  They're all waiting anxiously for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:25.16,Main,Fishwoman,0000,0000,0000,,Dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.16,0:05:26.49,Main,Fishkid,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:27.48,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.48,0:05:29.04,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, just go to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:32.05,Main,Fishkid,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.05,0:05:34.14,Main,Fishwoman,0000,0000,0000,,Dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.15,0:05:41.96,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Aladdin.  You're free too, just like they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.96,0:05:44.14,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,You can finally leave this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.14,0:05:45.86,Main,Aladdin,0000,0000,0000,,Jinbe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.86,0:05:50.96,Main,Aladdin,0000,0000,0000,,We will no longer be chased as former slaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.96,0:05:54.60,Main,Aladdin,0000,0000,0000,,We can even live peacefully with our families again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.02,0:05:58.97,Main,Aladdin,0000,0000,0000,,But, just like the Celestial Dragons' mark that was burned into our skin,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.97,0:06:04.18,Main,Aladdin,0000,0000,0000,,our deep hatred for the humans who made us into slaves and put us through that horrible ordeal...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.18,0:06:06.84,Main,Aladdin,0000,0000,0000,,will never fade.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.28,0:06:15.06,Main,Aladdin,0000,0000,0000,,I, too, understand Brother Ti's intentions\Nso well it hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.30,0:06:17.36,Main,Aladdin,0000,0000,0000,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.86,0:06:24.75,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that Boss Jinbe became\Na lap dog of the World Government...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.75,0:06:27.12,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Of the humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.12,0:06:30.87,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Is he forgetting who drove Tiger-san to his death?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.87,0:06:34.12,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,I've really misjudged Boss Jinbe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.61,0:06:44.02,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,I knew there were many citizens who thought less of me for joining the Seven Warlords.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.72,0:06:56.08,Main,Otohime,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to Jinbe's big decision,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:06:59.81,Main,Otohime,0000,0000,0000,,there is finally a connection\Nbetween fishmen and the World Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.81,0:07:04.19,Main,Otohime,0000,0000,0000,,In order to use this opportunity\Nto improve our relations with the humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:06.69,Main,Otohime,0000,0000,0000,,I will continue to work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:10.41,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,Still, even if it was to save his crewmates...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.41,0:07:13.99,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,Jinbe has taken on quite a heavy burden -jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.99,0:07:16.92,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,Should the World Government order him to,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.92,0:07:23.92,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,he will have to fight on their side,\Nregardless of his own feelings on the matter -jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:28.80,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,It's likely that he will have to cause bloodshed at times, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:33.32,Main,Otohime,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.  I will make sure\NJinbe's determination is not in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.83,0:07:35.55,Main,Otohime,0000,0000,0000,,I have to work hard too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.55,0:07:40.02,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,Don't overexert yourself, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:43.85,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,It would not do to have you spend another day in bed with a hangover -jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:45.11,Main,Otohime,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.21,0:07:55.95,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,And shortly after, an incident that would greatly change Queen Otohime's fate took place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.93,0:08:00.02,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,An uninvited guest dropped by...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.59,0:08:02.67,Main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuguu Palace!  Ryuuguu Palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.67,0:08:04.63,Main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Border Police!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.63,0:08:08.42,Main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,An enormous shipwreck is requesting emergency entrance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.60,0:08:12.38,Main,Right Minister,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?! \NNaturally, you have to let them in{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.38,0:08:13.93,Main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm not mistaken...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.14,0:08:20.35,Main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,a Celestial Dragon is onboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.70,0:08:21.89,Main,Right Minister,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:24.23,Main,Right Minister,0000,0000,0000,,King Neptune!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:26.19,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,A Celestial Dragon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.19,0:08:27.54,Main,Otohime,0000,0000,0000,,Grant him access!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.11,0:08:29.90,Main,Otohime,0000,0000,0000,,Send an emergency unit to the coast!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.92,0:08:30.39,Main,Guards,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.72,0:08:32.91,Main,Otohime,0000,0000,0000,,I will be there shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.91,0:08:33.79,Main,Right Minister,0000,0000,0000,,Otohime-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.48,0:08:38.25,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,What business does a Celestial Dragon have on the ocean floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.92,0:08:41.70,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,A Celestial Dragon's ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:44.16,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like it was attacked by a deep sea creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.16,0:08:50.21,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,What business do Celestial Dragons,\Nwho discriminate against us, have on the ocean floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.41,0:08:53.17,Main,Myosgard,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.31,0:08:59.56,Main,Myosgard,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!  Those spineless cowards all died on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:03.06,Main,Myosgard,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and bring me a mask, you pathetic fish-creatures!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.70,0:09:07.42,Main,Myosgard,0000,0000,0000,,This place reeks of fishmen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.62,0:09:12.94,Main,Myosgard,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and bring me a mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.95,0:09:16.67,Main,Myosgard,0000,0000,0000,,Save my life, you imbeciles!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:19.62,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Just how self-centered...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:21.95,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really the attitude\Nsomeone asking for help should have?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.91,0:09:26.28,Main,Myosgard,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.00,0:09:28.96,Main,Myosgard,0000,0000,0000,,Get me a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:30.45,Main,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the medical team?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.45,0:09:32.16,Main,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,They're here, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.16,0:09:34.21,Main,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,they're not sure what to do about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.21,0:09:36.03,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,We should kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:41.17,Main,Hody,0000,0000,0000,,The worst type of trash in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.17,0:09:43.69,Main,Vander Decken,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about those damn Warlords!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.69,0:09:51.36,Main,Vander Decken,0000,0000,0000,,Be it the World Government or whoever, I won't become anyone's underling just 'cause they ask me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.36,0:09:53.94,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,And that's what makes you our Captain Vander Decken.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:59.06,Main,Vander Decken,0000,0000,0000,,That Jinbe doesn't have what it takes to be a pirate of my caliber!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.06,0:10:00.66,Main,Vander Decken,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't have what it takes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.66,0:10:02.28,Main,Vander Decken,0000,0000,0000,,I presume!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.91,0:10:07.92,Main,Vander Decken,0000,0000,0000,,There sure is a lot of noise coming from the port.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.47,0:10:09.09,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.93,0:10:15.58,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, apparently a Celestial Dragon has come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.58,0:10:17.76,Main,Vander Decken,0000,0000,0000,,A Celestial Dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.76,0:10:21.56,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Seems he got here on a wrecked ship,\Nand he's now asking for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.36,0:10:24.24,Main,Vander Decken,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.24,0:10:26.14,Main,Vander Decken,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.44,0:10:34.09,Main,Myosgard,0000,0000,0000,,This wasn't supposed to happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.67,0:10:39.32,Flashbacks,Myosgard,0000,0000,0000,,What? My fishman slaves\Nhave returned to Fishman Island?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:41.57,Flashbacks,Myosgard,0000,0000,0000,,Why did that happen, My Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.17,0:10:44.53,Flashbacks,His Daddy,0000,0000,0000,,From what I hear, My Son,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.53,0:10:49.75,Flashbacks,His Daddy,0000,0000,0000,,the latest addition to the Seven Warlords of the Sea\N was a fishman named Jinbe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.29,0:10:51.42,Flashbacks,Myosgard,0000,0000,0000,,Jinbe?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.42,0:10:56.76,Flashbacks,His Daddy,0000,0000,0000,,The slaves who fled and joined the Sun Pirates,\Nwhich he was a part of,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.76,0:11:00.49,Flashbacks,His Daddy,0000,0000,0000,,were given a pardon by the Government, forgiven for the sin of running away,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.49,0:11:03.76,Flashbacks,His Daddy,0000,0000,0000,,and returned to their country, it seems, My Son.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:09.48,Flashbacks,Myosgard,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that the slaves that ran away from my house\Nare among them, My Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:12.22,Flashbacks,His Daddy,0000,0000,0000,,They must be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.22,0:11:17.36,Flashbacks,His Daddy,0000,0000,0000,,When I think about how they must be living\Nsuch carefree lives right now, I get really annoyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:21.24,Flashbacks,Myosgard,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll go get them back, My Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.24,0:11:25.74,Flashbacks,Myosgard,0000,0000,0000,,My fishman slave collection,\Nthat I spent so much money gathering!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:31.43,Main,Myosgard,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it... I didn't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.43,0:11:34.54,Main,Myosgard,0000,0000,0000,,that the deep seas were this terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:37.23,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!  What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.82,0:11:51.27,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see, Myosgard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:54.69,Main,Myosgard,0000,0000,0000,,You dare address me without honorifics... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:12:02.14,Main,Myosgard,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you are... my slaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.17,0:12:05.74,Main,Myosgard,0000,0000,0000,,Obediently come back to my home!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.74,0:12:08.24,Main,Myosgard,0000,0000,0000,,Who gave you permission to be free,\Ndamn fish-creatures?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:17.51,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop it, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.51,0:12:21.46,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,He's a Celestial Dragon!\NLay a hand on him, and your pardons will be void!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.01,0:12:24.97,Main,Myosgard,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, you fool!  Know your place!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:27.85,Main,Myosgard,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea who I am?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.85,0:12:30.27,Main,Myosgard,0000,0000,0000,,I am... I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:36.16,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Up on the surface, a Navy Admiral will immediately be dispatched if a Celestial Dragon is harmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.16,0:12:39.07,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only reason why everyone fears you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.90,0:12:43.18,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,However, this is Fishman Island, on the bottom of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.18,0:12:47.71,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,As long as the citizens here keep quiet, it won't matter what happens to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.71,0:12:49.24,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,It'll just be assumed you had an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.37,0:12:52.22,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.98,0:12:54.52,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,I won't say a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.52,0:12:55.72,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Neither will I!  Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.72,0:13:00.61,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,He's barely alive anyway!\NHe'll die if we just ignore him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.61,0:13:04.22,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Let him taste the pain you had to endure as slaves!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:05.33,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.33,0:13:06.73,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Let him suffer, and kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.73,0:13:08.07,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forgive him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.66,0:13:11.85,Main,Myosgard,0000,0000,0000,,What?  I am great...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.53,0:13:14.02,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I wanted to forgive...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.03,0:13:25.12,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one person I could never forgive!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.22,0:13:28.19,Main,Myosgard,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.67,0:13:29.82,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.82,0:13:30.69,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.69,0:13:36.87,Main,Otohime,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.87,0:13:38.79,Main,Myosgard,0000,0000,0000,,Damn fish-creatures!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.89,0:14:00.25,Main,Fishmen,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Queen Otohime!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.87,0:14:21.31,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Her Majesty's been shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.86,0:14:33.47,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Queen Otohime...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.92,0:14:37.85,Main,Otohime,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone... Please throw away your guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.25,0:14:42.19,Main,Otohime,0000,0000,0000,,The children are watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.50,0:14:51.57,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Aladdin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.23,0:14:54.73,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,What's this I heard\Nabout a shipwrecked Celestial Dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.73,0:14:56.54,Main,Aladdin,0000,0000,0000,,I only just got here myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.35,0:14:59.25,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Boss Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.07,0:15:03.42,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Mother raced out of the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:04.67,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.29,0:15:08.38,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother, who are these Celestial Dragons?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:11.02,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,They're humans, Shirahoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.02,0:15:12.05,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:18.27,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Out of all the humans in the world, they're among the scariest ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.27,0:15:21.82,Main,Aladdin,0000,0000,0000,,I heard several gunshots.  Let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.82,0:15:22.65,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:24.29,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Otohime-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.07,0:15:28.01,Main,Otohime,0000,0000,0000,,It only grazed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.01,0:15:29.65,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you protect him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:33.24,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what that man did to us in the past?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.16,0:15:39.75,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,He treated us worse than slaves, even worse than cattle!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.75,0:15:44.36,Main,Otohime,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear the screams of\Nyour hearts so clearly, it hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.65,0:15:48.00,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:49.23,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.89,0:15:57.01,Main,Otohime,0000,0000,0000,,I know it must be difficult for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.01,0:16:00.87,Main,Otohime,0000,0000,0000,,but your anger and hatred toward the humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.87,0:16:03.27,Main,Otohime,0000,0000,0000,,Do not pass it on to the children!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.24,0:16:09.11,Main,Otohime,0000,0000,0000,,Think of what they must face from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.68,0:16:16.89,Flashbacks,Tiger,0000,0000,0000,,So, I beg of you! {Copy-paste from 543}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.89,0:16:20.87,Flashbacks,Tiger,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell the people on our island anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.87,0:16:26.04,Flashbacks,Tiger,0000,0000,0000,,Not about the tragedy that befell us,\Nnor about our anger towards the humans. {End copy-paste from 453}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.24,0:16:29.42,Thoughts,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Brother Ti...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.39,0:16:42.29,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Look out, Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.54,0:16:45.90,Main,Myosgard,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:47.86,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!  Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:49.86,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.62,0:16:53.28,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.28,0:16:55.35,Main,Myosgard,0000,0000,0000,,Queen?  Whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.35,0:16:57.51,Main,Myosgard,0000,0000,0000,,As far as Celestial Dragons like myself are concerned,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.51,0:17:01.04,Main,Myosgard,0000,0000,0000,,the queen of some country of fish-creatures\Nis no different from the inferior commoners.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:02.50,Main,Myosgard,0000,0000,0000,,No, in fact she's even beneath them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.85,0:17:04.32,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.96,0:17:08.17,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.48,0:17:16.85,Main,Myosgard,0000,0000,0000,,You fools, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.29,0:17:20.49,Main,Myosgard,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and bring me a mask, and a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.49,0:17:21.77,Main,Myosgard,0000,0000,0000,,Or else...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.86,0:17:33.24,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.62,0:17:34.53,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.32,0:18:00.35,Main,Fishmen,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sea Kings?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.62,0:18:30.09,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,What... was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.77,0:18:32.86,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't just be a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.23,0:18:40.93,Thoughts,Otohime,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi... You couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.14,0:18:48.02,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.65,0:18:52.41,Thoughts,Decken,0000,0000,0000,,There is a legend passed down in my family...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.41,0:19:00.49,Thoughts,Decken,0000,0000,0000,,In the distant past, there lived a Mermaid Princess\Nwho possessed the sacred power to control Sea Kings!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.49,0:19:06.76,Thoughts,Decken,0000,0000,0000,,My forefather Vander Decken traveled to the ocean floor in pursuit of that legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.76,0:19:11.96,Main,Decken,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Honored forefather!  I have finally found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:15.32,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi is the legendary Mermaid Princess?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.32,0:19:17.27,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,You did it, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:20.84,Main,Decken,0000,0000,0000,,It would be bad if anyone else heard about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.84,0:19:26.06,Main,Decken,0000,0000,0000,,This is a secret legend, that only my family knows of...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:27.60,Main,Decken,0000,0000,0000,,I presume!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:30.76,Main,Decken,0000,0000,0000,,If I could freely control the Sea Kings and have them do my bidding,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.76,0:19:33.34,Main,Decken,0000,0000,0000,,everyone would have to do as I told them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.34,0:19:35.95,Main,Decken,0000,0000,0000,,I would be able to take whatever I wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:39.82,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:42.03,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Are we going to kidnap Princess Shirahoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.56,0:19:45.83,Main,Decken,0000,0000,0000,,First, I must become the princess's husband!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.83,0:19:48.07,Main,Fishmanz,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whaaaaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.07,0:19:50.83,Main,Fishmanz,0000,0000,0000,,But Princess Shirahoshi is still a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.83,0:19:53.79,Main,Decken,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, and therein lies the problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:19:58.11,Main,Otohime,0000,0000,0000,,Aladdin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.88,0:20:03.39,Main,Aladdin,0000,0000,0000,,I will... treat his wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.39,0:20:04.80,Main,Otohime,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.11,0:20:07.97,Main,Aladdin,0000,0000,0000,,And yours as well, Otohime-sama, as soon as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.66,0:20:15.00,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Some weeks later, after the Celestial Dragon's treatment was complete and his life had been saved,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.00,0:20:17.36,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,and he was about to leave for his homeland...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.36,0:20:21.67,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Queen Otohime made an astonishing move.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.26,0:20:35.17,Main,Myosgard,0000,0000,0000,,Remember this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.17,0:20:40.48,Main,Myosgard,0000,0000,0000,,All the tactlessness and rudeness that I, a World Noble, had to endure here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.48,0:20:44.25,Main,Myosgard,0000,0000,0000,,Damn fish-creatures!\NI swear I will make you regret them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.88,0:20:48.05,Main,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,We saved his life, so why does he resent us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.05,0:20:53.63,Main,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Our country gave him\Nthe ship and crew to take him home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.63,0:20:55.31,Main,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,How can he talk to us like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.31,0:20:59.96,Main,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,We shouldn't let him leave.\NHe'll just put the island in even greater danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.47,0:21:03.57,Main,Otohime,0000,0000,0000,,Please, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.53,0:21:06.73,Main,Otohime,0000,0000,0000,,We still have some unfinished business, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.28,0:21:10.33,Main,Otohime,0000,0000,0000,,That being the case,\NI will accompany you to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.29,0:21:12.58,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,To the surface?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.58,0:21:14.46,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,That's crazy!  Otohime-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.02,0:21:15.75,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.16,0:21:18.31,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,Wait -jamon, Otohime!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.31,0:21:20.53,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,I will not allow you to do something so self-centered!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.53,0:21:24.59,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,If you absolutely must settle things with the Nobles, then I will go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.45,0:21:31.14,Main,Otohime,0000,0000,0000,,You are the king and a great knight,\NI'm sure you'd never be captured by the humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.14,0:21:32.56,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,That's why it should be me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.56,0:21:36.02,Main,Otohime,0000,0000,0000,,No.  If someone as strong as you went,\Nit would be meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.77,0:21:42.11,Main,Otohime,0000,0000,0000,,If the weak cannot travel there and return safely,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.11,0:21:46.35,Main,Otohime,0000,0000,0000,,we cannot prove to our citizens that the surface is safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:51.20,Main,Otohime,0000,0000,0000,,That is why I, who am weaker than most,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.20,0:21:53.20,Main,Otohime,0000,0000,0000,,must go to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.29,0:21:55.66,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.66,0:21:56.54,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.54,0:21:58.18,Main,Fishkid,0000,0000,0000,,Otohime-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.18,0:22:00.64,Main,Fishkid,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going somewhere, Otohime-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.24,0:22:04.38,Main,Neptune,0000,0000,0000,,Otohime...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.38,0:22:05.77,Main,Otohime,0000,0000,0000,,Believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.31,0:22:09.94,Main,Otohime,0000,0000,0000,,in the wife you chose, and in the humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.11,0:22:19.13,Main,Myosgard,0000,0000,0000,,She's merely the queen of\Nthese fish-creatures!  Such conceit!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.07,0:22:27.28,Main,Fukaboshi,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.28,0:22:29.91,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.12,0:22:35.65,Main,Aladdin,0000,0000,0000,,Jinbe...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.65,0:22:39.26,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody could have possibly stopped her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.26,0:22:42.67,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,We can only believe in her, and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.67,0:22:49.81,Main,Crowd,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your Majesty!  Please, be safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.90,0:22:49.81,Secondary,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Otohime-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.81,0:22:53.28,Main,Shirahoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.32,0:23:09.20,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,When people finally start to share Otohime's dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.20,0:23:12.16,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,the sound of a single gunshot\Nresounds across Fishman Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.16,0:23:13.34,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.34,0:23:14.12,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,A Sudden Tragedy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.78,0:23:15.83,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,A Bullet that Seals the Future
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.83,0:23:18.00,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!
